than 5 years.

276
00:14:50,642 --> 00:14:53,043
How did you think that
was gonna go, Tommy?

277
00:14:54,379 --> 00:14:56,079
About like that.

278
00:14:57,248 --> 00:14:59,133
Ok, so we took care
of that. Good call.

279
00:14:59,135 --> 00:15:00,634
Now we can make up
for lost time.

280
00:15:00,636 --> 00:15:02,136
If you're not
too sick of fish,

281
