288
00:15:31,584 --> 00:15:32,916
If anybody's making it
out of here,

289
00:15:32,918 --> 00:15:34,334
it's gonna be him.

290
00:15:36,755 --> 00:15:39,473
I'm so sorry. I thought
I'd have more time.

291
00:15:39,475 --> 00:15:41,475
I'm not the man you
think I am.

292
